data.description: Don't miss the opportunity to be walking distance from Mansfield Elementary School. This 3 bedroom 2 full bath beauty boasts tons of charm and uniqueness. The eat-in kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, an upgraded faucet, and backsplash. The primary en-suite offers a room-size closet with custom shelving. You'll also enjoy a beautiful soaking tub and oversized spa-style tiled shower. This beauty offers custom built bunkbeds perfect for kids, but can be easily removed if not needed. Enjoy family game nights gathered around the family room fireplace. Home has a bonus room perfect for office space or extra storage. This home is also perfect for entertaining, it features an oversized enclosed patio with recessed lighting and a ceiling fan. There's also plenty of room to cook out on the unenclosed portion of the patio. Home offers a large backyard with inground firepit and storage shed.
